- **Fonts**: Configured `display: swap` for `next/font`.
- **Bundle**: Standard Next.js optimizations active.

## Accessibility
- **Alt Text**: Every image includes descriptive alt text.
- **Labels**: All form inputs have associated visible `<label>` elements.
- **Aria**: Icon-only buttons (Menu, Socials, Scroll Top) have `aria-label`.
- **Focus**: Inputs have visible focus states (`ring-[#C5A059]`).
- **Skip Link**: Added skip-to-content link in Navbar.
- **HTML**: Semantic tags (`header`, `main`, `footer`, `section`, `nav`) used correctly.

## SEO
